I"	<h3 id="troubleshooting-port-not-available">Troubleshooting: Port not available</h3>

<p>While sleeping, the port will not be available via the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">USB</code> port. Hence, a delay has been added by blinking the LED to make time for uploading firmware in development.</p>

